============================================================
    mindG4 - Geant4 simulation of the MIND calorimeter    
============================================================

$Id: README 329 2009-08-24 09:55:22Z jmalbos $



0. Prerequisites
-----------------
MindG4 depends on several third-party libraries. Make sure
you have them installed:

- CLHEP,
- Geant4.9.2 (or later),
- OpenGL and X11 (for visualization),
- BHEP
- and ROOT.

SCons (http://www.scons.org/) is used for compiling and
building the package. At least version 1.0.0 is required.
SCons depends on Python (version >1.5.2).


